Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan blunders over Marcos election
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xpl5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Feb 1986
Reagan statement about 'fraud on both sides' of Philippines election seen as huge blunder which could have left opposition to Marcos in a dangerous position. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less